'''''X-Wing Rogue Squadron Special''''' is a one-shot issue of the [[Star Wars Legends|''Star Wars'' Legends]] [[Star Wars comic books|comic book]] series ''[[Star Wars: X-Wing Rogue Squadron]]''. It was written by [[Ryder Windham]], illustrated by [[John Nadeau]], and first published on [[August 1]], [[1995]] by [[Dark Horse Comics]].

The issue was available exclusively as a marketing premium for [[Wikipedia:Apple Jacks|Apple Jacks]] cereal, and it was distributed through [[Wikipedia:Kellogg's|The Kellogg Company]]. A digital edition was published by [[Marvel Comics]] in [[2015]].

==Publisher's summary==
